00002850                           822  ; -----------------------------------------------------------------------------
00002850                           823  DMMALLOC
00002850                           824  ; SEARCHES THE FIRST FREE (SYS OWNED) SLOT, ASSIGNS TO THE SPECIFIED OWNER
00002850                           825  ; AND RETURNS A POINTER TO THE CORRESPONDING DATA (SLOT ADDRESS + 2)
00002850                           826  ; INPUT    - D0.W : ID TO ASSIGN
00002850                           827  ; OUTPUT   - A0   : POINTER TO THE DATA OR 0 IF NOT FREE SPACE
00002850                           828  ; MODIFIES - NONE (ASIDE OF OUTPUT)
